graph TD
    A[BIOS] --> B(Master Boot Record<br/>MBR)
    B --> C{Active Partition Boot Sector}
    C --> D["`start.s` & `bstart.s`<br/>(Initial 16-bit real mode setup)"]
    D --> E["`boot.c`<br/>(Main C bootloader)"]
    E --> F["Reads /etc/default/boot"]
    E --> G["Presents boot prompt"]
    G --> H["`load.c`<br/>(Loads kernel e.g., /stand/unix)"]
    H --> I["Transition to 32-bit Protected Mode"]
    I --> J[Kernel Initialization<br/>`main()`]

    style J fill:#lightgreen,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
